result.title: My Soft and Plush Rug (5'3 x 7'6)
result.body: Add a pop of color to any living space with this rug. Machine-made from soft polypropylene synthetic fiber, this indoor rug has a classic rectangular shape and a generous one-inch pile height.

result.title: Wooden Lantern
result.body: Make your next garden party jump with this set of two red wooden lanterns designed to light up an exciting night.

result.title: 4-light Bamboo Pendant
result.body: Close your eyes and picture your favorite city at sunset. Think dark buildings silhouetted against the ethereal glow of the fading sun, and you will see the inspiration for this bamboo pendant.
